3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20doing%20it%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20beating%20the%20guy%20next%20to%20you%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20what%20hiring%20managers%20are%20looking%20for.%20It's%20not%20a%20numbers%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20students%20can%20probably%20pick%20up%20technical%20skills%20and%20important%20soft%20skills%20from%20just%20one%20internship%2C%20said%20Sim%2C%20the%20former%20banker.%20Sim%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehiring%20managers%20also%20care%20about%20candidates'%20soft%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20look%20out%20for%20is%20whether%20you%20have%20the%20social%20skills%20to%20talk%20to%20customers.%20Banking%20is%20really%20a%20sales%20job.%20You%20need%20to%20win%20the%20mandate%20from%20the%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Sim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20some%20students%20like%20NUS'%20Loh%2C%20forging%20ahead%20remains%20the%20goal%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20it%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20effort-wise%2C%20there%20really%20is%20no%20limit%20for%20me.%20Would%20I%20rather%20enjoy%20now%20but%20be%20mediocre%20in%20life%20or%2C%20worse%2C%20suffer%20later%3F%20Or%20would%20I%20rather%20grind%20now%20but%20gain%20the%20potential%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20future%3F%20The%20latter%20resonates%20with%20me%20infinitely%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Loh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-fight-hunger-games-style-for-top-banking-jobs-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715643781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66139ffc3f923f7dab055a8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-students-fight-hunger-games-style-for-top-banking-jobs-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singaporean%20college%20students%20say%20they're%20pulling%20out%20all%20the%20stops%20and%20stacking