p%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20study%20of%2024%2C109%20men%20found%20low%20testosterone%20linked%20to%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20early%20death.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20findings%20suggest%20the%20hormone%20is%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20health%20and%20longevity%20for%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20whether%20hormone%20therapy%20boosts%20longevity%20but%20habits%20like%20diet%20and%20exercise%20can%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETestosterone%20levels%20may%20be%20an%20important%20indicator%20of%20longevity%20for%20men%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20of%20more%20than%2024%2C000%20men%20from%20around%20the%20world%20found%20that%20low%20testosterone%20was%20linked%20to%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20dying%20early%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20published%20May%2013%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acpjournals.org%2Fdoi%2F10.7326%2FM23-2781%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnnals%20of%20Internal%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Western%20Australia%20worked%20with%20a%20global%20team%20of%20scientists%20to%20compare%20baseline%20testosterone%20levels%20to%20health%20outcomes%20using%20data%20from%20previous%20studies%20on%20older%20men%2C%20ranging%20in%20age%20from%20late%2040s%20to%20mid-70s%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20dying%20early%2C%20from%20any%20cause%2C%20among%20men%20with%20a%20low%20baseline%20testosterone%20level%20%E2%80%94%20defined%20as%20below%20213%20nanograms%20per%20deciliter%20(ng%2FdL).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmen-should-know-testosterone-levels-by-age-30-urologist-says-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHealthy%20testosterone%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20range%20from%20260%20to%20900%20ng%2FdL%20depending%20on%20age%2C%20a%20urologist%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%20also%20found%20that%20men%20with%20very%20low%20testosterone%20levels%20(below%20153%20ng%2FdL)%20had%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20dying%20from%20cardiovascular%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20are%20observational%2C%20which%20means%20the%20researchers%20found%20a%20pattern%20but%20didn't%20directly%20show%20that%20low%20testosterone%20causes%20a%20higher%20mortality%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20new%20study%20helps%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20mixed%20research%20around%20longevity%20and%20the%20hormone%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20boosting%20low%20testosterone%20with%20hormone%20therapy%2C%20an%20independent%20researcher%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acpjournals.org%2Fdoi%2F10.7326%2FM24-0875%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeditorial%20published%20alongside%20the%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e94a8bfd-bf4a-4c2b-942d-110d797b9ab5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETestosterone%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20the%20longevity%20and%20biohacking%20field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20study%20focused%20on%20endogenous%20testosterone%2C%20the%20kind%20naturally%20occurring%20in%20the%20body%2C%20not%20hormone%20therapy.%20However%2C%20understanding%20how%20testosterone%20may%20help%20or%20hurt%20longevity%20could%20make%20big%20waves%20in%20the%20booming%20hormone%20therapy%20market%20of%20products%20and%20services%20advertised%20to%20help%20men%20reclaim%20their%20youth%20with%20pills%2C%20patches%2C%20injections%2C%20or%20gels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20entrepreneurs%20touting%20testosterone%20as%20an%20anti-aging%20panacea%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftestosterone-parties-silicon-valley-hormone-boosting-bio-hack-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiohacking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20science%20to%20try%20to%20optimize%20health%20and%20extend%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20yet%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20whether%20supplementing%20testosterone%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-aging-treatments-that-actually-work-vs-scams-2023-4%23no-testosterone-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there's%20some%20evidence%20to%20the%20contrary.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fdrugs%2Fdrug-safety-and-availability%2Ffda-drug-safety-communication-fda-cautions-about-using-testosterone-products-low-testosterone-due%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%20previously%20issued%20a%20warning%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20testosterone-boosting%20treatments%20may%20raise%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20attack%20or%20stroke%2C%20although%20subsequent%20research%20has%20since%20found%20no%20significant%20increase%20in%20heart%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216779cee-55b1-4bf0-acb9-7eac2de86b65%5C%22%3ESigns%20of%20low%20testosterone%2C%20and%20what%20to%20do%20about%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETestosterone%20levels%20tend%20to%20drop%20with%20age%20and%20can%20also%20dip%20in%20response%20to%20health%20conditions%20and%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommon-signs-low-testosterone-according-to-doctors-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELow%20testosterone%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20cause%20symptoms%20such%20as%20fatigue%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20and%20disruptions%20in%20mood%20and%20libido.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELifestyle%20factors%20such%20as%20eating%20a%20nutritious%20diet%2C%20getting%20enough%20exercise%2C%20and%20managing%20stress%20are%20linked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-increase-testosterone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20testosterone%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20can%20also%20play%20a%20role%20in%20preventing%20heart%20disease%20and%20other%20chronic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreatments%20like%20hormone%20replacement%20therapy%2