l%20directors%20their%20first%20breaks.%20He%20received%20an%20honorary%20Academy%20Award%20in%202009%20%26quot%3Bfor%20his%20unparalleled%20ability%20to%20nurture%20aspiring%20filmmakers%20by%20providing%20an%20environment%20that%20no%20film%20school%20could%20match.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%202017%2C%20chief%20video%20correspondent%C2%A0Graham%C2%A0Flanagan%20sat%20down%20with%20Corman%20in%20his%20Los%20Angeles%20office%20for%20a%20wide-ranging%20conversation%20about%20his%20storied%20career.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20this%20extended%20version%20of%20the%20interview%20has%20been%20published.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECorman%20is%20credited%20with%20helping%20launch%20the%20careers%20of%20actors%20such%20as%20Jack%20Nicholson%20as%20well%20as%20Academy%20Award-winning%20filmmakers%20like%20Martin%20Scorsese%2C%20James%20Cameron%2C%20Francis%20Ford%20Coppola%2C%20and%20Jonathan%20Demme.%20Corman%20hired%20these%20directors%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20their%20careers%20to%20helm%20low-budget%20features%20that%20the%20filmmakers%20have%20acknowledged%20as%20learning%20experiences%20they%20applied%20in%20their%20later%20larger-scale%20productions.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20fact%2C%20many%20of%20these%20directors%20hired%20Corman%20in%20small%20acting%20roles%20in%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Godfather%20Part%20II%2C%26quot%3B%20(Coppola)%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Silence%20of%20the%20Lambs%26quot%3B%20(Demme)%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BApollo%2013%26quot%3B%20(Ron%20Howard).%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Corman%20shares%20myriad%20lessons%20learned%20while%20working%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20for%20more%20than%2060%20years.%20He%20talks%20about%20producing%20a%20movie%20that%20was%20never%20released%20based%20on%20Marvel's%20%26quot%3BFantastic%20Four%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20he%20made%20a%20unique%20deal%20with%20Universal%20Pictures%20for%20the%20rights%20to%20the%20title%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fast%20and%20the%20Furious%2C%26quot%3B