0Srinagar%20Seat%2C%20Highest%20In%2035%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Srinagar%20constituency%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20voted%20on%20Monday%20to%20choose%20its%20next%20representative%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20--%20the%20first%20election%20there%20since%20the%20general%20election%20of%202019.%20And%20the%20voting%20figure%20broke%20all%20records.%20In%20absence%20of%20any%20boycott%20call%20from%20separatists%20or%20fear%20of%20violence%2C%2038%20per%20cent%20people%20came%20out%20to%20vote%20--%20a%20first%20in%2035%20years%20and%20highest%20since%201989.%C2%A0%20Srinagar%20had%20recorded%2014%20per%20cent%20polling%20in%20the%20last%20general%20election.%20PK%20Pole%2C%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20J%26amp%3BK%20the%20figure%20may%20go%20up%20once%20the%20final%20data%20is%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20general%20election%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20lost%20its%20statehood%20and%20the%20special%20status%20granted%20under%20the%20Constitution's%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20applauded%20the%20people%20and%20attributed%20the%20unexpected%20turnout%20to%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20especially%20like%20to%20applaud%20the%20people%20of%20Srinagar%20Parliamentary%20constituency%20for%20the%20encouraging%20turnout%2C%20significantly%20better%20than%20before.%20The%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20has%20enabled%20the%20potential%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20to%20find%20full%20expression.%20Happening%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20it%20is%20great%20for%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20his%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWould%20especially%20like%20to%20applaud%20the%20people%20of%20Srinagar%20Parliamentary%20constituency%20for%20the%20encouraging%20turnout%2C%20significantly%20better%20than%20before.%20The%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20has%20enabled%20the%20potential%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20to%20find%20full%20expression.%20Happening%20at%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2DvSCnXFKR%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2DvSCnXFKR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1790066344169189709%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pole%20said%20there%20were%20four%20key%20reasons%20for%20high%20turnout%20after%20decades%20of%20poll%20boycott%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20first%20important%20factor%20is%20improvement%20in%20situation%20over%20last%20few%20years.%20Second%20is%20effective%20campaigning%20by%20the%20candidates%20and%20the%20number%20of%20candidates%20who%20were%20in%20fray%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSVEEP%20activities%20has%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20creating%20awareness%20among%20the%20people.%20Above%20all%2C%20it%20is%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20who%20have%20realised%20that%20ballot%20is%20the%20only%20answer%20to%20ensure%20sustainable%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pulwama%20district%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Srinagar%20seat%2C%20had%20recorded%20just%20one%20per%20cent%20polling%20in%20the%20last%20parliament%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20leader%20Ghulam%20Mohi-Ud-Din%20Mir%2C%20who%20has%20survived%20over%20a%20dozen%20terror%20attacks%2C%20said%20today's%20vote%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%20hundreds%20of%20political%20workers%20including%20his%20father%2C%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20choosing%20democracy%20over%20mil