p-chinese-migrants-forming-an-army-in-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F110090167.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thieves%20Drill%20Hole%20In%20Wall%20Of%20Delhi%20Shop%2C%20Rob%20Jewellery%2C%20CCTV%20Cameras%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThey%20drilled%20a%20hole%20in%20a%20wall%20of%20a%20shop%20in%20a%20busy%20market%20and%20stole%20jewellery%20and%20cash%20worth%20lakhs.%20Not%20just%20jewellery%2C%20they%20also%20took%20away%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20with%20them.%20The%20real-life%20heist%20at%20a%20Delhi%20jewellery%20store%20was%20reminiscent%20of%20scenes%20from%20the%20popular%20Netflix%20show%20'Money%20Heist'%20but%20a%20real-life%20heist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20of%20the%20shop%20at%20Chandni%20Chowk's%20Dariba%20Kalan%20market%20got%20the%20shock%20of%20his%20life%20this%20morning%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20ornament%20showcase%20was%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20old%20shop.%20When%20I%20tried%20to%20open%20the%20shutter%20this%20morning%2C%20I%20couldn't%2C%20I%20called%20a%20man%20for%20help.%20When%20he%20lifted%20the%20shutter%2C%20he%20said%20that%20all%20the%20jewellery%20on%20the%20counter%20was%20gone.%20When%20the%20shutter%20was%20lifted%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20showcase%20was%20empty%20and%20there%20was%20a%20gaping%20hole%20in%20one%20of%20the%20walls%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kirit%20Bhai%20Soni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soni%20speculated%20that%20the%20thieves%20gained%20entry%20through%20an%20adjacent%20vacant%20shop%2C%20drilling%20their%20way%20into%20his%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20thieves%20had%20made%20away%20with%20nearly%20Rs%201%20lakh%20cash%20and%2014%20kg%20of%20silver%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20traders%20in%20the%20area%20are%20shocked%20at%20the%20incident%20as%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20hustle-bustle%20at%20the%20Dariba%20Kalan%20market%20even%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20shopkeeper%20insisted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpre-planned%26quot%3B%20crime%20and%20also%20highlighted%20the%20lack%20of%20security%20arrangements%20at%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20looks%20like%20a%20pre-planned%20crime.%20This%20couldn't%20have%20been%20done%20without%20a%20recce%20because%20they%20have%20drilled%20a%20hole%20into%20the%20wall%20and%20taken%20away%20the%20cameras%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deepak%20Soni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20not%20many%20CCTV%20cameras%20here%20(at%20the%20market).%20The%20ones%20that%20are%20here%20don't%20work.%20There's%20a%20security%20guard%20also%20but%20he%20is%20almost%20always%20unavailable%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20and%20said%20they%20were%20scanning%20the%20nearby%20CCTV%20cameras.%20The%20police%20called%20forensic%20experts%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20incident%20happened%20last%20year%20when%20a%20thief%20broke%20into%20a%20jewellery%20store%20in%20south%20Delhi's%20Jangpura%20and%20escaped%20with%20ornaments%20worth%20crores.%20He%20entered%20the%20terrace%20of%20a%20four-storey%20building%20next%20to%20the%20store%2C%20reached%20the%20ground%20floor%20where%20the%20strongroom%20was%20located%2C%20disconnected%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20and%20drilled%20a%20hole%20into%20the%20wall%20to%20enter%20the%20locker.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715615160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvlrmcphk_delhi-heist_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fthieves-drill-hole-in-wall-of-delhi-shop-rob-jewellery-cctv-cameras-5655702%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20drilled%20a%20hole%20in%20a%20wall%20of%20a%20shop%20in%20a%20busy%20market%20and%20stole%20jewellery%20and%20cash%20worth%20lakhs.%20Not%20just%20jewellery%2C%20they%20also%20took%20away%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20with%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F