0he%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%20emergent%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20leader%20then%20and%20now%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20native%20has%20prided%20himself%20on%20displaying%20integrity%20even%20in%20the%20most%20sticky%20spots.%20Early%20on%2C%20he%20resolved%20never%20to%20see%20transfers%20as%20a%20punishment.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20transfer%20is%20part%20of%20your%20career%20and%20as%20a%20servant%20of%20your%20nation%2C%20it%20is%20your%20duty%20to%20do%20it%20with%20utmost%20commitment%20and%20professionalism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%20five%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20not%20only%20has%20he%20stayed%20true%20to%20those%20words%2C%20but%20has%20found%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348647%2Fcancer-shelter-in-india-access-life-ankeet-dave-girish-nair-children-paediatric-care-in-mumbai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurpose%20in%20his%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%20in%20the%20Haldwani%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBlazing%20a%20trail%20in%20conservation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20head%20of%20the%20research%20wing%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20conservation%20of%20threatened%20plant%20species%2C%20the%2050-year-old%20officer%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20biodiversity%20protection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20crucial%20in%20this%20area.%20Uttarakhand%20has%20over%2043%20types%20of%20different%20forests%20and%20three%20major%20agro-climate%20zones%3A%20tropical%2C%20temperate%20and%20alpine.%20The%20altitude%20of%20the%20place%20ranges%20from%20300%20m%20up%20to%20the%206%2C800%20m%20high%20Nanda%20Devi%20Peak.%20As%20you%20can%20see%2C%20the%20flora%20here%20experiences%20a%20very%20diverse%20climate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5