atimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-hugs-alia-bhatts-bodyguard-at-airport-bhatts-kapoors-care-for-raha-as-alia-ranbir-work-imran-khan-on-criticism-of-ira-khans-podcast-top-5-entertainment-news-of-the-day%2Farticleshow%2F110088413.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varanasi%20Welcomes%20PM%20With%20Drums%2C%20Conches%20And%20Roads%20Awash%20With%20Saffron%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVaranasi%20turned%20out%20in%20its%20festive%20best%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20a%20mega%20roadshow%20this%20evening%20in%20the%20constituency%20from%20where%20he%20is%20seeking%20a%20third%20term.%20The%20snaking%20lanes%20of%20the%20country's%20oldest%20city%20saw%20around%20a%20hundred%20stages%20built%20over%20a%206-km%20stretch.%20As%20his%20convoy%20rolled%20through%20the%20roads%20that%20turned%20a%20sea%20of%20saffron%20with%20millions%20of%20buntings%20and%20cutouts%2C%20cultural%20programmes%20were%20held%20on%20the%20stages%20and%20slogans%20in%20support%20of%20the%20VIP%20candidate%20rang%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20lined%20the%20road%2C%20carrying%20special%20drums%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20city's%20reigning%20deity%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Many%20were%20seen%20dressed%20as%20Lord%20Shiva%20and%20Lord%20Krishna.%20The%20sound%20of%20conches%2C%20dhols%20and%20damrus%20filled%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20the%20journey%20that%20started%20from%20the%20celebrated%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20end%20later%20this%20evening%20at%20the%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20one%20of%20the%20holiest%20pilgrim%20centres%20in%20the%20country.%20PM%20Modi%20will%20also%20go%20to%20seek%20blessings%20from%20Baba%20Vishwanath%2C%20BJP%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20route%20was%20marked%20with%20several%20stops%20at%20including%20Sant%20Ravidas%20Gate%2C%20Assi%2C%20Shivala%2C%20Sonarpura%2C%20Jangambadi%20and%20Godaulia.They%20are%20part%20of%20the%20100%20points%20at%20which%20people%20from%20different%20communities%20have%20gathered%20to%20welcome%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20holding%20laser%20shows.%20The%20party%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20temples%20and%20religious%20leaders%20to%20canvass%20support%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20organising%20drone%20laser%20shows%20at%20the%20city's%20Dashashwamedh%20Ghat%20after%20the%20Ganga%20aarti%20in%20the%20evening.%20More%20than%201%2C000%20drones%20are%20used%20to%20showcase%20the%20party's%20development%20work%20in%20Varanasi%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roadshow%20comes%20ahead%20of%20tomorrow's%20filing%20of%20nomination%20by%20PM%20Modi%2C%20who%20won%20from%20the%20constituency%20with%20a%20huge%20margin%20for%20the%20time%20in%202014.%20Twelve%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20present%20in%20Varanasi%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20scopped%20up%20a%20staggering%206.7%20lakh%20votes%2C%20trouncing%20his%20closest%20competitor%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Shalini%20Yadav.%20who%20got%201.9%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Varanasi%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20election%20on%20June%201.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715606940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffa74u86c_narendra-modi-varanasi_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-varanasi-welcomes-pm-with-drums-conches-and-roads-awash-with-saffron-5654693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Varanasi%20turned%20out%20in%20its%20festive%20best%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20