e%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nagesh%20alleged%20H%20Revanna%20was%20arrested%20unnecessarily%2C%20as%20he%20could%20have%20been%20released%20after%20questioning%20and%20called%20back%20for%20interrogation%20whenever%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20allegation%20of%20the%20survivor%20being%20forced%20or%20trapped.%20There%20was%20no%20demand.%20HD%20Revanna%20is%20a%20politician%20and%20there%20are%20political%20reasons%20behind%20his%20arrest.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20April%2029%20and%20the%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20May%202.%20There%20was%20no%20kidnap%20or%20illegal%20detention.%20The%20survivor%20was%20a%20maid%20at%20HD%20Revanna's%20residence%20and%20the%20kidnap%20charges%20don't%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20Police%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20HD%20Revanna%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20kidnapping%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20survivors%20of%20the%20sex%20video%20scandal%20involving%20his%20son%2C%20on%20Friday%20after%20the%20woman's%20son%20had%20registered%20a%20missing%20complaint%2C%20accusing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20relative%20Satish%20Babu%20was%20named%20the%20second%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20and%20was%20arrested%20from%20Mysuru%20district%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715606940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fk0ge3t4g_hd-revanna_625x300_21_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjds-hd-revanna-in-judicial-custody-over-kidnapping-case-gets-bail-5654600%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20MLA%20HD%20Revanna%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20a%20local%20court%20in%20a%20kidnapping%20case.%20His%20son%2C%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20sex%20scandal%20case%20linked%20to%20leaked%20obscene%20videos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http