%2F110088685.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Japanese%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20build%20up%20a%20strategy%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March%202024%20for%20decarbonization%20and%20Industrial%20policy%20targeting%202040.%20%E2%80%8BThe%202040%20strategy%20is%20expected%20to%20refine%20last%20year's%20plan%20and%20provide%20more%20predictability%20of%20long-term%20investments%20while%20enhancing%20the%20competitiveness%20of%20domestic%20companies%20and%20fostering%20economic%20growth%2C%20Yojiro%20Hatakeyama%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20Industrial%20Science%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20Environment%20Policy%20Bureau%20at%20the%20industry%20ministry.%20told%20reporters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-to-craft-2040-strategy-of-decarbonization-and-industrial-policy%2Farticleshow%2F110088685.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-to-craft-2040-strategy-of-decarbonization-and-industrial-policy%2Famp_articleshow%2F110088685.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-to-craft-2040-strategy-of-decarbonization-and-industrial-policy%2Famp_articleshow%2F110088685.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20Asked%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Will%20You%20Get%20Married%26quot%3B.%20He%20Smiled%20And%20Said...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20from%20Raebareli%2C%20is%20campaigning%20to%20defend%20the%20family%20bastion%20-%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20reached%20the%20constituency%20with%20his%20sister%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20to%20participate%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20rallies%20since%20he%20filed%20nominations%20for%20the%20seat.%20It%20was%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20first%20rally%20in%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20concluding%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20asked%20his%20supporters%20whether%20they%20had%20any%20questions.%20A%20supporter%20in%20the%20crowd%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20are%20you%20getting%20married%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20Congress%20leader%20paused%20for%20a%20few%20seconds...smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJaldi%20karni%20padegi%26quot%3B%20(Now%2C%20I%20have%20to%20get%20married%20soon).%20Mr%20Gandhi%20waved%20at%20the%20crowd%20while%20his%20sister%20smiled%20and%20clapped%20and%20he%20walked%20off%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20ended%20his%20speech%2C%20he%20called%20his%20sister%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20dais.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20expressed%20his%20appreciation%20for%20her%20efforts%20in%20the%20Raebareli%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20touring%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20the%20election%20and%20my%20sister%20is%20spending%20time%20here%2C%20a%20big%20thanks%20to%20her%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20not%20contesting%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20is%20rallying%20for%20her%20brother%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20party%20loyalist%20and%20close%20aide%2C%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20in%20Amethi.%20The%20two%20seats%20combined%20were%20considered%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20party%20until%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20defeated%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20previous%20general%20elections%20in%202019%20and%20took%20the%20seat%20away%20from%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20surrounding%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20ended%20when%20Congress%20fielded%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20from%20the%20former%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20from%20the%20latter.%20The%20BJP%20has%20taunted%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20choice%20and%20Ms%20Irani%2C%20the%20current%20MP%20from%20Amethi%20even%20called%20Mr%20Sharma%20a%20%26quot%3Bproxy%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Gandhis%20would%20have%20fought%20themselves%20and%20not%20fielded%20a%20proxy%20if%20they%20felt%20they%20could%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20welcoming%20our%20guests.%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20not%20field%20anyone%20from%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20Amethi%20signifies%20that%20it%20has%20accepted%20defeat%20even%20before%20voting%20takes%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20actor-turned-politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20had%20won%20Amethi%20in%202004%2C%202009%2C%20and%202014%2C%20but%20a%20defeat%20to%20Ms%20Irani%20in%202019%20reduced%20the%20Congress's%20UP%20footprint.%20He%20had%20contested%20Wayanad%20in%202019%20as%20a%20second%20seat%20and%20won%20it%20to%20retain%20his%20MP%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaebareli's%20tryst%20with%20Congress%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20first%20general%20elections%20in%201952%20when%20the%20seat%20was%20held%20by%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20won%20the%20Raebareli%20seat%20in%201952%20and%20then%20again%20in%201957.%20After%20he%20died%20in%201960%2C%20the%20Congress%20fielded%20RP%20Singh%20in%20the%20by-elections%20and%20retained%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonia%20Gandhi%20picked%20Raebareli%2C%20a%20seat%20she%20won%20for%20four%20consecutive%20terms.%20In%20February%202024%2C%20when%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20not%20contest%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20she%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Raebareli%20electorate%2C%20who%20supported%20her%20for%20two%20decades.%20%26quot%3BMy%20family%20in%20Delhi%20is%20incomplete%3B%20it's%20you%20all%20in%20Raebareli%20who%20complete%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20former%20Congress%20president.%20She%20added%20that%20her%20family's%20ties%20with%20Raebareli%20run%20deep%20and%20she%20received%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsa