www-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-69000698.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-69000698.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20'Connected%2C%20But%20Maintaining%20Distance'%3A%20Indian%20Students%20Amid%20US%20Protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fa68tl4bs_us-campus-protests_625x300_04_May_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EImaandari%20se%20dekha%20jaye%20to%20dar%20hai%20ki%20yahan%20se%20utha%20kar%20phekh%20denge%2C%20deport%20kar%20denge%20%3C%2Fem%3E(to%20be%20honest%2C%20there's%20fear%20that%20they'll%20throw%20us%20out%2C%20deport%20us)%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20graduate%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oregon%20says%20as%20he%20talks%20about%20the%20fear%20of%20%26quot%3Bserious%20consequences%26quot%3B%20that%20his%20%26quot%3Bstudent%20visa%20issues%26quot%3B%20may%20entail%20amidst%20the%20ongoing%20protests%20at%20his%20college.%20For%20an%20Indian%20national%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20who%20has%20strived%20hard%20to%20get%20to%20the%20country%2C%20the%20choice%20between%20getting%20involved%20in%20the%20current%20protests%20against%20Israeli%20action%20in%20Gaza%20or%20staying%20aloof%20is%20not%20very%20difficult.%20%26quot%3BIn%20principle%2C%20I%20can%20relate%20to%20them.%20But%20I%20can't%20take%20a%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20wishing%20to%20stay%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nationwide%20wave%20of%20pro-Palestine%20demonstrations%20has%20roiled%20American%20campuses.%20Students%20and%20faculty%20are%20demanding%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20and%20calling%20for%20divestment%20of%20university%20endowments%20from%20companies%20that%20have%20ties%20with%20Israel.%20In%20the%20crackdown%20on%20these%20demonstrations%2C%20university%20administrations%20have%20called%20in%20police%20to%20remove%20protest%20encampments%3B%20hundreds%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20activists%20have%20been%20arrested.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20reports%20of%20arrests%20or%20suspensions%20of%20Indian%20students%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20A%20Minority%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Indian%20students%20are%20today%20witnessing%20the%20largest%20US%20student%20movement%20in%20decades%2C%20but%20they%20stand%20mostly%20on%20the%20sidelines.%20Referring%20to%20Indian%20participation%2C%20Jayati%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20at%20University%20of%20Massachusetts%20in%20Amherst%2C%20notes%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20at%20the%20encampment.%20It's%20difficult%20to%20generalise%2C%20but%20certainly%20I%20would%20say%20it's%20a%20minority.%26quot%3B%20Terming%20the%20actions%20of%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20and%20their%20approach%20to%20these%20protests%20%26quot%3Bhigh-handed%26quot%3B%2C%20Ghosh%20says%20that%20students%20from%20India%20face%20different%20repercussions%20compared%20to%20American%20citizens.%20%26quot%3BThe%20consequences%20are%20really%20heavy%20for%20them%20because%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20to%20get%20here%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20expenses%20for%20those%20who%20are%20paying%20for%20their%20education%20themselves.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20parental%20pressure%20-%20%26quot%3Byou%20get%20your%20degree%20and%20come%20home%26quot%3B%20kind%20of%20a%20thing.%20My%20students%20have%20mentioned%20these%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20involvement%20has%20deterred%20'progressive'%20students%20even%20though%20they%20believe%20in%20the%20'democratic%20right%20to%20protest'.%20Being%20scared%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bimpact%20on%20his%20fellowship%26quot%3B%2C%20Sushil%2C%20a%20student%20at%20Washington%20University%20in%20St%20Louis%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20that%20the%20American%20police%20system%20is%20very%20fair.%20We%20have%20seen%20police%20brutality%20against%20black%20protesters%20in%202017.%26quot%3B%20The%20possibility%20of%20arrest%20weighs%20on%20their%20minds.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20are%20in%20trouble%2C%20no%20one%20comes%20to%20help%20you%2C%20so%20why%20should%20I%20join%20the%20protests%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Right%20To%20Protest%26quot%3B%20And%20Other%20Misinformation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20students%20enter%20the%20US%20on%20F-1%20or%20J-1%20visas%2C%20which%20are%20granted%20based%20on%20their%20college%20admissions.%20New%20Jersey-based%20immigration%20attorney%20Rupal%20Parikh%20says%20that%20a%20student's%20visa%20is%20linked%20to%20their%20college%20enrollment.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20follow%20campus%20rules%20for%20peaceful%20protest%20and%20get%20expelled%2C%20that%20is%20going%20to%20absolutely%20impact%20whether%20you%20can%20continue%20to%20be%20here%20to%20finish%20your%20education%20because%20your%20student%20visa%20would%20be%20cancelled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20maintaining%20their%20legal%20status%20in%20the%20international%20student%20community%20have%20led%20to%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20about%20rights%20and%20consequences.%20An%20Indian%20graduate%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Philadelphia%2C%20is%20convinced%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20student%20visa%20doesn't%20allow%20us%20the%20right%20to%20protest.%20Officially%2C%20only%20citizens%20have%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20in%20this%20country%20so%20those%20can%20be%20grounds%20for%20deportation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20whether%20foreigners%20have%20the%20legal%20right%20to%20protest%2C%20Parikh%20clarifies%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20a%20right%20to%20protest%2C%20whether%20you're%20a%20citizen%20student%20or%20a%20foreign%20national.%26quot%3B%20She%20says%20that%20a%20visa%20is%20impacted%20only%20in%20rare%20instances.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20student%20gets%20arrested%2C%20usually%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20impact%20their%20student%20visa%2C%20unless%20it%20was%20something%20very%20serious%2C%20say%2C%20murder%20or%20some%20sort%20of%20egregious%20felonious%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJob%20Market%20Fears%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20job-worthiness%20also%20impact%20the%20decision-making%20of%20these%20young%20scholars.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20participated%20in%20rallies.%20The%20encampment%20was%20on%20campus%2C%20so%20of%20course%20you%20walk%20by%20and%20observe.%20I%20do%20relate%20to%20the%20cause%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20fear%20because%20the%20university%20is%20checking%20IDs%20on%20campus.%20Their%20policies%20might%20hamper%20not%20only%20the%20visa%20status%20of%20students%20involved%2C%20but%20also%20job%20prospects%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sparsh%20Maheshwari%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20encampment%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20was%20disbanded%20by%20the%20police%20on%20May%2010.%20Several%20areas%20have%20been%20cordoned%20off%2C%20and%20six%20students%20were%20told%20to%20go%20on%20mandatory%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalancing%20academics%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20those%20Indian%20students%20who%20are%20protesting.%20Pragya%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20Ann%20Harbor%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20are%20not%20supportive%20of%20these%20protests.%20They%20want%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20studies%2C%20which%20I%20do%20agree%20with.%20During%20the%20finals%20%5Bexams%5D%20weeks%2C%20when%20we%20were%20at%20the%20encampment%2C%20I%20sat%20there%20and%20studied.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20have%20a%20big%20career%20and%20that%20I%20have%20the%20money%20and%20the%20prestige%20to%20make%20more%20of%20a%20change.%20However%2C%20if%20I%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20some%20level%20of%20change%20while%20I'm%20here%2C%20that%20I%20will%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20Behind%20The%20Scenes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20a%20few%20international%20students%20like%20Indian-Canadian%20Tarana%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20whose%20passion%20for%20the%20cause%20trumps%20fears.%20%26quot%3BIndian%20and%20other%20international%20students%2C%20in%20general%2C%20stayed%20away%20from%20protests%20initially%20because%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20fear-mongering%20around%20our%20ability%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20country%20if%20we%20partake%20in%20protests.%20But%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%20or%20so%2C%20I've%20seen%20a%20lot%20more%20Indian%20students%20showing%20up%20at%20protests%20on%20our%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20participating%20graduate%20students%20do%20so%20because%20they%20have%20'more%20safeguards'%20than%20undergraduates.%20Karthik%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20grad%20students%20have%20more%20protections%20because%20we%20are%20unionised.%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20or%20four%20years%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20PhD%20students%20in%20the%20US%20have%20unionised%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20more%20protection%20to%20speak%20up.%20The%20university%20can't%20unilaterally%20decide%20to%20fire%20or%20take%20unjust%20action%20against%20you.%26quot%3B%20He%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BHence%2C%20many%20undergraduate%20students%20contribute%20behind%20the%20scenes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelping%20keep%20a%20'robust%20protest'%20up%20requires%20organising%20literature%2C%20communications%20and%20social%20media%2C%20as%20well%20as%20taking%20care%20of%20logistics%20and%20coordination%20with%20groups%20at%20other%20universities%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20Aalok%20Tyagi%2C%20a%202023%20graduate%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20who%20continues%20to%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20student%20body%2C%20says%20%26quot%3BI%20help%20relay%20messages%20to%20a%20larger%20body%20through%20group%20chats%20of%20interested%20students%2C%20our%20Instagram%20page%2C%20and%20internal%20communication%20with%20the%20student%20government%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20have%20their%20support.%20This%20is%20a%20movement%20that%20the%20university%20doesn't%20support.%20So%2C%20it's%20chaotic.%20Hence%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20have%20as%20many%20allies%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracing%20The%20Money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20research%20and%20dissemination%20of%20information%20too.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I'm%20involved%20in%20the%20back%20end%20of%20things.%20On%20university%20campuses%20in%20the%20US%2C%20discrimination%20happens%20not%20only%20if%20you're%20a%20Palestinian%20student%20but%20even%20if%20you're%20mildly%20supportive%20of%20Palestine%2C%20which%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20certain%20American%20laws%2C%20including%20the%20Civil%20Rights%20Act.%20Many%20of%20us%20are%20trying%20to%20see%20whether%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20use%20that%20law%20to%20get%20universities%20to%20take%20a%20less%20hostile%20approach.%26quot%3B%20He%20and%20a%20group%20of%20students%20have%20also%20been%20researching%20university%20investments.%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20universities%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20which%20they%20have%20invested%20in%20Israeli%20companies%20and%20military%20defence%20contractors.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20where%20exactly%20it%20is%20they've%20invested%20it.%20Based%20on%20the%20anti-apartheid%20movement%20in%20South%20Africa%20of%20the%201970s-'80s%2C%20we've%20understood%20that%20it%20might%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20target%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20pre-medical%20student%2C%20Pragya%20becomes%20the%20camp%20medic.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20CPR%20training%2C%20so%20I'm%20the%20pretty%20medical%20here.%20People%20have%20been%20hurt.%20I%20have%20wrapped%20a%20sprained%20ankle%2C%20helped%20with%20allergy%20reactions.%20We%20got%20tear%20gassed%20the%20other%20day%20so%20we%20made%20sure%20people%20were%20okay%20after%20that.%26quot%3B%20Her%20role%20involves%20planning%2C%20generating%20funds%2C%20communicating%20with%20media%2C%20and%20being%20at%20the%20encampment%2C%20including%20during%20law%20enforcement%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20like%20Pragya%20know%20the%20advantages%20that%20come%20with%20being%20an%20American%20citizen%20on%20campus.%20She%20is%20an%20Indian-American%2C%20which%20affords%20her%20the%20freedom%20and%20%26quot%3Bprivilege%20of%20participation%26quot%3B%20without%20worrying%20about%20deportation.%20In%20turn%2C%20American%20students%20are%20protective%20of%20international%20students%20and%20consider%20%26quot%3Brisk%20assessment%20for%20arrest%26quot%3B%20while%20planning%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtecting%20Each%20Other%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20students%20themselves%20decide%20that%20in%20situations%20where%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20arrested%2C%20only%20those%20who%20are%20citizens%20or%20permanent%20residents%20get%20involved.%20They%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20are%20more%20vulnerable%20are%20not%20in%20the%20direct%20line%20of%20fire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZainab%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20it's%20kind%20of%20unavoidable%20as%20we%20can%20never%20really%20control%20how%20the%20police%20or%20the%20administration%20choose%20to%20react%2C%20we%20as%20a%20community%20protect%20as%20many%20of%20our%20members%20as%20we%20can%2C%20including%20international%20students%2C%20as%20they%20have%20more%20at%20stake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5C