s%20annual%20water%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20monsoon%2C%20we%20save%20up%20to%2035%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater.%20We%20use%20the%20harvested%20rainwater%20for%20cleaning%20and%20gardening%20purposes.%20Whereas%2C%20we%20use%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20once%20a%20week%20and%20tanker%20supply%20thrice%20a%20month%20for%20kitchen%2C%20bathing%2C%20dishes%2C%20and%20laundry%20purposes%2C%20and%20water%20cans%20for%20drinking%20needs.%20We%20are%20a%20family%20of%20four%20and%20rainwater%20takes%20care%20of%20half%20of%20our%20annual%20water%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20garden%20with%20350%20plants%20amid%20water%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECloser%20to%20their%20rainwater%20harvesting%20tank%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20maintained%20a%20lush%20green%20garden%20of%20350%20plants%20comprising%20ornamental%2C%20flowering%2C%20succulents%2C%20handfuls%20of%20greens%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20ayurvedic%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-2-1715150689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amid%20water%20crisis%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Suma%20are%20able%20to%20nurture%20their%20flourishing%20garden%20with%20over%20350%20plants.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-2-1715150689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-2-1715150689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-2-1715150689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBengaluru-water-2-1715150689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBenga