lutions%20to%20address%20water%20scarcity%20and%20RWH%20is%20a%20low-hanging%20fruit.%20I%20like%20it%20because%20it%20is%20decentralised%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20single%20point%20of%20failure%2C%20and%20some%20versions%20like%20groundwater%20recharging%20aren%E2%80%99t%20terribly%20expensive%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20less%20than%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20properties%20with%20water%20connections%20have%20implemented%20rainwater%20harvesting%3B%20and%20solving%20the%20water%20crisis%20in%20Bengaluru%20will%20require%20multiple%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20conservation%20involves%20commitment%20and%20investment%20in%20terms%20of%20money%2C%20time%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%20Also%2C%20in%20the%20current%20fast-paced%20city%20life%2C%20where%20we%20depend%20a%20lot%20on%20domestic%20help%20to%20run%20day-to-day%20chores%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20find%20support%20staff%20who%20are%20obliged%20to%20adopt%20similar%20practices%20to%20help%20conserve.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20is%20needed%20is%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20options%20available%20for%20lowering%20environmental%20impact%20and%20then%20make%20an%20educated%20choice%20based%20on%20personal%20context%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20suggests%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fwater-famine-in-bengaluru-2930568%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWater%20famine%20in%20Bengaluru%3F%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20A%20Ravindra%20for%20Deccan%20Herald%2C%20Published%20on%2011%20March%202024.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fbe