r%20my%20care.%20Yet%2C%20upon%20returning%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20these%20children%20confront%20challenges%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20at%20such%20tender%20ages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20a%20distressing%20incident%20during%20their%20summer%20vacation%20when%20she%20encountered%20one%20of%20her%20students%20begging%20on%20the%20streets.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20children%20who%20stay%20with%20us%20leave%20for%20summer%20vacations%20to%20their%20homes.%20While%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them%20the%20best%20life%20here%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20poverty%20they%20were%20born%20into%20hits%20hard.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20vacation%20days%20that%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20students%20begging.%20It%20was%20heart-wrenching%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20upset.%20I%20spoke%20to%20their%20parents%2C%20but%20the%20mother%20simply%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98How%20will%20they%20eat%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20beg%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FThe-Better-India%2FSupport-Srotoshwini-Trust%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Juin%20realised%20the%20stark%20contrast%20the%20children%20experience%20in%20their%20transition%20from%20hostel%20to%20home.%20It%20stressed%20the%20gravity%20of%20her%20work%2C%20as%20it%20dawned%20upon%20her%20that%20good%20education%20serves%20as%20their%20only%20ticket%20to%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20reflecting%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20hunger%2C%20Juin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20young%20boy%20under%20our%20care%20who%20confessed