have%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20at%20least%20five%20times%20in%20their%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20manufacturers%2C%20Himanshu%20Jain%2C%20who%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20Ankush%20for%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20work%20on%20credit%20with%20offline%20distributors.%20This%20meant%20that%20we%E2%80%99d%20get%20payments%20only%20after%2030%20to%2045%20days.%20They%20would%20also%20buy%20sarees%20in%20bulk%20and%20there%20was%20no%20surety%20if%20all%20sarees%20would%20be%20sold.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20would%20return%20to%20us%20after%20a%20month%20or%20so%20and%20dump%20all%20the%20unsold%20sarees.%20The%20onus%20to%20sell%20these%20would%20fall%20on%20us.%20But%20with%20Deeva%2C%20we%20get%20orders%20only%20after%20the%20consumer%20has%20placed%20an%20order%2C%20and%20we%20get%20payments%20in%207%20to%2010%20days.%20Here%2C%20my%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2025%20percent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20to%20make%20Deeva%20a%20big%20brand%2C%20Ankush%20wanted%20to%20appear%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%20Even%20though%20he%20could%20not%20make%20it%20to%20season%202%2C%20he%20made%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98sharks%E2%80%99%20in%20season%203.%20The%20impact%20of%20the%20episode%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20he%20observed%20a%20boost%20of%20six%20times%20in%20his%20business%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Ankush%20now%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20business%20of%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20enter%20into%20export%20in%20at%20least%2010%20countries%2C%20and%20open%20offline%20stores%20in%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20feel%20I%20have%20achieved%20very%20big.%20It%20was%20through%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20that%20we%20started%20getting%20meals%20three%20times%20a%20day.%20M